This folder contains the support code for the STM32F746G-DISCO board
(MB1191B).


STM32CubeF7 Firmware Package
============================
This directory contians parts of STM32CubeF7 1.6.0, which are
relevant to the STM32F746G-DISCO board. To preserve compatibilty
with STM32CubeF7, this directory preserves the sub-directory
structure of STM32CubeF7, so the relative paths should work for
the full version of STM32CubeF7 as well.
